                        "text": "Comment \u201cSHIRT\u201d for a Google Map link of the store!\n\nLet me put you onto one of the coolest stores in Tokyo called #FFFFFFT (color code for white + T)\n\nThe world\u2019s first white t-shirt speciality store that sells, you guessed it, white tees only. \n\n@shirothunter is the genius behind this spot and he\u2019s seriously obsessed with white tees (obsessed enough to open an entire store for them). If you have the chance to visit on the weekends, his ability to find you the best white tee shirt is impressive.\n\nJust like Japanese denim, these tees are made with the same high quality production standards and attention to detail you won\u2019t find anywhere else on the planet. \n\nHis motto: If you step inside, you\u2019ll find at least one white tee that fits your body perfectly. So, if you\u2019re in Tokyo, don\u2019t sleep on this store!\n\u2014\nIG: @fffffft_sendagaya\nOwner: @shirothunter\nOPEN SAT 12pm-7pm / SUN 12pm-6pm\n\n#tokyo #whitetees #shirotee #tokyotravel #tokyostyle #fashion #madeinjapan #japanesegifts"
                    }
